{
  "stem": "10587.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they already had older people, because all the young people they took to fight both-- now they had to fight the American front as well.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was a very sad time, too, because they were telling us, the SS troopers were telling us that the Americans are going to lose the war because your father, Roosevelt, died.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was during the time when-- and-- and they were-- just to give us that extra coup de grace.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so they, every day, they would remind us about that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, we took-- they took us to one forest one time, and we were strafed by the American Mustangs.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We lost a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was-- this is the march, I think, where I was wearing the-- the clogs, the wooden clogs, because now I remember I was-- my feet were hurting me so much.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was sitting-- sitting behind a tree-- they have those old trees-- and-- and-- and the Mustangs would come down very low, and they would throw the concussion mines, which explode above ground and kill everything in sight.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the wehrmacht at that time was using horses as well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They confiscated all the horses wherever they could.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- and-- and so I took off a shoe, and I was ready to take off the other shoe, and lo and behold, they came down with those mines and-- and-- and the bullets that were very explosive when they hit-- you know, that they used.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there were bodies flying all over, and portion of-- portion of bodies, and it was a bloody scene.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then they-- some of the mines hit the horses, and some of the wehrmacht because we were very close by, so we--",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
